### Get Available Properties for All Entity Types
GET {{baseUrl}}/reconcile/properties

### Get Available Properties for Location Entity Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/reconcile/properties?type=location

### Get Available Properties for Site Entity Type  
GET {{baseUrl}}/reconcile/properties?type=site

### Get Available Properties for Taxon Entity Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/reconcile/properties?type=taxon

### Test Entity Preview (use FULL URI from reconciliation results)
# Note: The preview endpoint expects the full URI starting with id_base (e.g. https://w3id.org/sead/id/)
# For locations, the path segment is "place".
GET {{baseUrl}}/reconcile/preview?id=https://w3id.org/sead/id/location/100

### Test Site Preview (use FULL URI from reconciliation results)
# For sites, the path segment is "site".
GET {{baseUrl}}/reconcile/preview?id=https://w3id.org/sead/id/site/22

